snippet.textDisplay: Loved this video and all your content its really been helping me. Im going through and extremely dark and challenging time in my life right now and honestly barely hanging on but videos like this your others help keep my mind distracted so i dont have to feel or think about all the horrible things that have happened in my life recently. I just wanna say thank you for all your content you and jenna. Your probably tired of hearing this but when will you guys be putting out detroit on YouTube (i know you arent streaming and i understand why) for me detroit become human helped me tremendously get through some really bad shit bc of the adrenaline rush it would give me i didnt have time to think or feel. And honestly when you guys started playing it i ended up getting it and playing it myself bc you guys made it look so fun and it was around this time my grandma got really really sick and one of my best friends died from a freak accident he was only 23 with a baby and a fiance. I was losing my mind all i could think about was my grandma and my best friend and i couldnt breathe i would have huge panic attacks bc i knew i was going to loose my grandma soon too and i was afraid that i wouldnt be able to handle all of that loss. Your playthrough with jenna on Detroit and me playing that game got me through so that i didnt self harm or worse bc i really didnt know how i was going to make to through(to get away from the emotional pain it's hard for ppl to understand but its what used to work for me and my depression until i got put on antidepressants) i understand you guys are discouraged about playing the last part but please dont be i accidentally killed one of my favorite characters too (at the end) which does really suck but its such a beautiful and fun game after that point when you killed connor and u can always redo that part if you want. I understand if you guys dont want to play it anymore though there was a lot of jerks who put you down. i just had to ask one more time bc i LOVE the way you guys are playing (im an aries too and i love your aries energy lol) even if you guys dont play i just want to say thank you for posting what did post and all the videos you guys post on the regular its really been helping me even if its only for 10-15 mins like i really didnt think i would laugh again but your videos and jennas get me out of my own head so i can laugh. So thank you. Thank you so much.
